author: COMSOL
description:
This model illustrates the effect of oxygen and hydrogen formation and recombination on the performance and self-discharge of an electrochemical capacitor with an aqueous electrolyte.

A load cycle consisting of mixed constant current pulses and rest periods at open circuit is studied.
